name: never know
description:
sketch on paper but processed by photocopy  
21,0 x 29,7 cm    
2018
Original work and photo by dutadpt



This may be my first experimental work in 2018. I made it using a photocopier, first I made a sketch, and I took a photo of up to 50 copies. and this is the one that I think is according to my will, although 49 more copies are also my process and I still keep it as my personal archive.
